Reasoning: The paper deals with the design of a robust lattice alignment method for MIMO interference channels with imperfect channel knowledge. This involves optimization problems related to signal processing, information theory, and communication engineering. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely sub-categories include cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
